      Q(4,I)=(A*EN+B)*1.D-21     
      QATT(1,I)=Q(4,I)                                       
   40 Q(5,I)=0.0                                                        
      Q(6,I)=0.0  
C                                                            
C SUPERELASTIC VIB1        
