C      
C IONISATION CALCULATION                                                                 
   40 DO 41 J=1,NION
      PEQION(J,I)=0.0
   41 QION(J,I)=0.0
C IF ENERGY LESS THAN 5KEV CALCULATE TOTAL COUNTING AND GROSS IONISATION
