C 1 TO 2% OF THE EXPERIMENTAL VALUES IN PURE GAS AND ARGON MIXTURES.
C THE TOWNSEND IS WITHIN 5% OF THE MEASUREMENTS OF YOSHIDA UP TO 2000TD
C
C THE X-SECTION DATA BASE HAS BEEN EXTENDED TO 1 GEV. 
